<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM6.5.4">
<l>uṟiyār veṇṇe yuṇṭu ralōṭuṅ kaṭṭuṇṭu</l>
<l>veṟiyār kūntal piṉṉai poruṭṭāṉ veṉṟāṉūr</l>
<l>poṟiyār maññai pūmpo ḻiltōṟum naṭamāṭa</l>
<l>naṟunāṇ malarmēl vaṇṭicai pāṭum naṟaiyūrē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The city of him who, having eaten ghee from the pot nets</l>
<l rend="indent">and having been tied to a mortar,</l>
<l>Conquered a bull for the sake of the young girl  with fragrant tresses,</l>
<l>Is Naṟaiyūr where bees on the [new] day’s fragrant flowers sing melodies,</l>
<l>As in every blossoming garden plumed peacocks perform dances.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
